Properties.Caption: Просмотр остатков на бюджетных счетах
Properties.Tag: Select [K_BD].[CBD] As [Код бюджета], [Apps_Groups].[GroupName] As [Группа], [K_TD].[CTD] As [Тип документа], [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [DOC].[DU_R] As [Дата утверждения распорядителя], [K_TS].[CTS] As [Текущий счет], [K_BN].[NBN] As [Наименование банков], Max([K_LSR].[NLSR]) As [ПБК], Sum([REP].[SUMM01]) As [Графа 01] From ((((((((((([REP] With (NoLock) Inner Join [DOC] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[DOCID]=[DOC].[DOCID])) Inner Join [K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[Apps_GroupsID]=[Apps_Groups].[Apps_GroupsID])) Inner Join [K_BD] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_BDID]=[K_BD].[K_BDID])) Left Join [K_LSR] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[ID3]=[K_LSR].[K_LSRID])) Inner Join [K_TS] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[ID1]=[K_TS].[K_TSID])) Inner Join [K_BN] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[ID2]=[K_BN].[K_BNID])) Inner Join [K_PERIOD] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[K_PERIODID]=[K_PERIOD].[K_PERIODID])) Inner Join [K_TD_SUB] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[K_TD_SUBID]=[K_TD_SUB].[K_TD_SUBID])) Inner Join [K_TD] With (NoLock) On ([K_TD_SUB].[K_TDID]=[K_TD].[K_TDID])) Where [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[Apps_GroupsID]=GetApps_GroupsID() And [K_TD_SUB].[CTD_SUB]='01' And [REP].[SUMM_TYPE]=0 And |0 Group by [K_BD].[CBD], [Apps_Groups].[GroupName], [K_TD].[CTD], [DOC].[CDOC], [DOC].[DU_R], [K_TS].[CTS], [K_BN].[NBN], [K_LSR].[K_LSRID] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр остатков на бюджетных счетах
